com.thedemgel.regions.annotations

Class OnTickParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thedemgel.regions.annotations.OnTickParser

  • public class OnTickParser
extends Object
    Parser to handle OnTick annotation. Any class that has a method with OnTick annotation attached needs to implement Tickable interface.
